# Invite Feature Environment Variables

## Required for all invite methods:
# TWILIO_ACCOUNT_SID and TWILIO_AUTH_TOKEN should already be configured

## For SMS invites:
TWILIO_FROM=+1234567890

## For WhatsApp invites:
# Use Twilio WhatsApp Sandbox number for testing
TWILIO_WHATSAPP_FROM=+14155238886

## For Email invites:
# Mailgun configuration should already be set in your YAML config file
# Additionally, you can set the from email address:
MAILGUN_FROM_EMAIL=invites@yourdomain.com
# Example mailgun config in yaml:
# mailgun:
#   apiKey: your-mailgun-api-key
#   domain: mg.yourdomain.com

## Optional - Firebase Dynamic Links:
# FIREBASE_DYNAMIC_LINK_DOMAIN=flash.page.link
# APP_INSTALL_URL=https://flash.app/download
# ANDROID_PACKAGE_NAME=com.flash.app
# IOS_BUNDLE_ID=com.flash.app